'''Planetary commandant'''<ref name="J2">{{JournalCite|2|The Free-Trader's Guide to Sevarcos}}</ref> or '''Imperial Commandant'''<ref name="J12">{{JournalCite|12|Festival of High Winds}}</ref> was the title given to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] officer who was in charge of the [[Spice/Legends|spice]] [[Mining/Legends|mining]] operations on [[Sevarcos II]]. The planetary commandant oversaw both military and political affairs on the planet and had direct access to all military material. Planetary Commandant [[Velpar Raftin]] served in this position during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].<ref name="J2" />

